  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[Digivolve]Lv.6 w/[Leopardmon]\_in its name w/o [X Antibody]\_trait:
    Cost 1 \n\n[When Digivolving] [Main] [Once Per Turn] You may play 1 green Digimon
    card from your hand with the play cost reduced by 4. If a card with [Leopardmon]\_in
