    it by 3.\n[Your Turn] [Once Per Turn] When one of your Digimon is played, you
    may return 1 of your opponent\u2019s 5000 DP or lower Digimon to the hand. For
    each of your other Digimon, add 3000 to the maximum DP this effect can choose."
